@timestamp = {{$timestamp}}

### 启动方式（两个终端）：
# 终端1：REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379 node examples/express/cross-redis-a.js
# 终端2：REDIS_URL=redis://127.0.0.1:6379 node examples/express/cross-redis-b.js

### A：打开 SSE（alice）
GET http://localhost:3004/sse?userId=alice
Accept: text/event-stream

### A：发起任务（A -> B -> Redis 回推 -> A 下发）
POST http://localhost:3004/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "alice",
  "payload": { "msg": "work please", "time": "{{timestamp}}" }
}
